description:
Madison tells fortunes for a living… Apparently though she isn’t good enough to predict The Master’s arrival… or she might have tried to run.

The Master Transforms her into a robot… He takes away any Future she may have had!

Now she is his Fembot Slut Forever! She will be trained into the perfect sex machine!
title: Fortunetellers Folly... Now Madison is The Master's Robot Slut
